ARM: brcmstb: select ARCH_DMA_ADDR_T_64BIT for LPAE

Broadcom STB (BRCMSTB) has some 64-bit capable DMA and therefore needs
dma_addr_t to be a 64-bit size.  One user is the Broadcom SATA3 AHCI
controller driver.

